title: Zygor 1-80 Alliance and Horde In-game Guides!
description:

It is fully functional and decreases you leveling time in WoW by giving you step by step instruction without having to Alt + Tab out to read! It also comes with Tom Tom which acts like a GPS to finding your quests faster! So this is one of the FEW Zygor 1-80 Guides that WORK. This IS COMPATABLE WITH WotLK! Enjoy and please help seed! :)

This also inclues an EXCLUSIVE Death Knight leveling guide and Talent Sheet! It also comes with a detailed Inscription Leveling Guide as well! Enjoy!
